c-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-quan-ly-lop-hoc-tro-thu-dac-luc-cua-giao-vien\/#dinh_nghia_cho_phan_mem_quan_ly_lop_hoc\" >\u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a cho Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd L\u1edbp h\u1ecdc<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-quan-ly-lop-hoc-tro-thu-dac-luc-cua-giao-vien\/#cach_phan_mem_quan_ly_lop_hoc_co_the_mang_lai_loi_ich_cho_lop_hoc_cua_ban\" >C\u00e1ch ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc sinh m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung, v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0o l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc sinh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o h\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\u00ean lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 trao quy\u1ec1n b\u1edfi gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean trong c\u00e1c l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng minh. V\u1eady th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc?<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dinh_nghia_cho_phan_mem_quan_ly_lop_hoc\"><\/span>\u0110\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a cho Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd L\u1edbp h\u1ecdc<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean t\u1ea1o ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1m thu h\u00fat h\u1ecdc sinh tham gia t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/p>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf quy\u1ec1n truy c\u1eadp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 trang web g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung tr\u00ean c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n cung c\u1ea5p c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecdc sinh t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u00e0. Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u00f3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0nh vi v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i n\u00e2ng cao.<\/p>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp (LMS) v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1ecdc sinh (SIS) c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc, cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5 huynh nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft s\u00e2u s\u1eafc h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 h\u00e0nh vi v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh m\u1ee5c kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-11468 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-26-at-15.19.35-800x240.jpg\" alt=\"Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd L\u1edbp h\u1ecdc\" width=\"763\" height=\"229\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-26-at-15.19.35-800x240.jpg 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-26-at-15.19.35-768x230.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-26-at-15.19.35-600x180.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Screen-Shot-2022-08-26-at-15.19.35.jpg 980w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 763px) 100vw, 763px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach_phan_mem_quan_ly_lop_hoc_co_the_mang_lai_loi_ich_cho_lop_hoc_cua_ban\"><\/span>C\u00e1ch ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ol>\n<li>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb v\u00e0o c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n: C\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc cung c\u1ea5p cho gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean CNTT c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u00ean c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/li>\n<li>T\u0103ng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c: V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y tham gia nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/li>\n<li>D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1eeb xa: Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eefng n\u1ed9i dung li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy c\u1eadp trong th\u1eddi gian h\u1ecdc.<\/li>\n<li>Ki\u1ec3m tra ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i: Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng tab, kh\u00f3a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f3a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ki\u1ec3m tra.<\/li>\n<li>Truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t nhanh ch\u00f3ng: Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eafn tin tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng.<\/li>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u01a1\u0323 ho\u0323c sinh: C\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 gi\u01a1 tay \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o sinh vi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap khi h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 h\u1ecd \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u.<\/li>\n<li>C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c: Chia s\u1ebb m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh cho ph\u00e9p c\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc sinh, sinh vi\u00ean. Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m n\u00e0y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb li\u00ean k\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c h\u1ecdc sinh.<\/li>\n<li>Uy\u1ec3n chuy\u1ec3n: Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp, bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, t\u1eeb xa v\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p.<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111a n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng: C\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e1m m\u00e2y ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh.<\/li>\n<li>N\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean: V\u1edbi c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed1 v\u00e0 phi\u1ebfu b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh, ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m b\u1edbt c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd r\u01b0\u1eddm r\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-11469 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/img-ngoai-ngu-1-367x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"367\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/img-ngoai-ngu-1-367x400.jpg 367w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/img-ngoai-ngu-1-735x800.jpg 735w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/img-ngoai-ngu-1-768x836.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/img-ngoai-ngu-1-600x653.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/img-ngoai-ngu-1.jpg 846w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 367px) 100vw, 367px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1c l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/h3>\n<p>Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p INNO Inclass+ cung c\u1ea5p cho c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc bao g\u1ed3m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng n\u00eau tr\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i \u00edch to l\u1edbn cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ph\u00e2n h\u1ec7 l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<p>\u25a0 Inclass+ for Multimedia Classroom: Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc \u0111a ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n<\/p>\n<p>\u25a0 Inclass+ for Smart Classroom: Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m ph\u00f2ng h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng minh<\/p>\n<p>\u25a0 Inclass+ for Language Classroom: h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng h\u1ecdc ngo\u1ea1i ng\u1eef<\/p>\n<p>T\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1\u00a0Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y\u00a0&amp; qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng minh. <a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/phan-mem-giang-day-va-quan-ly-lop-hoc\/\">T\u1ea0I \u0110\u00c2Y<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc sinh m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung, v\u00e0 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0o l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc. Nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a l\u1ea1i c\u00e1ch h\u1ecdc sinh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc. Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea3m&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":11469,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-11467","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11467","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11467"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11467\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":11471,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11467\/revisions\/11471"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/11469"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11467"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=11467"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=11467"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}